overview: Suffering. Chaos. Ugliness. Mayhem. From the day Kevin Steen, Jimmy Jacobs, and Steve Corino cemented their alliance over the fallen body of Davey Richards those were their goals and Ring of Honor their unfortunate victim. No soul on the ROH roster was safe from the wrath of those three men and with the  ROH World Title in their possession, the battle was on to save the soul of ROH from those poised to bring it down.
title: ROH: ROH vs SCUM
